item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】PACK - Charmed (1998) Complete Series Soundtrack [FLAC/MP3] {WEB/CD}
item.description:
Track List source - imgur.com/pSh19af

I've been personally collecting these for years. I've been able to find over 95% of the list, whether from my own cd's or downloaded from P2P/streaming platforms. For some reason, a few found on Tidal were only downloadable in MP3/M4A. I have no control over that.

Tracks marked with red dot - found in either FLAC or MP3. MOST ARE FLAC. Unmarked tracks have not been found in decent rip format. Some of the songs came from 1-hit-wonder artists over 20 years ago who didn't make it and so they were impossible to find today.

Traditional songs like "When The Saints Go Marching In" and Piper/Leo's wedding song have not been included, as there are far too many covers to know which version they actually used.

Individual songs have been zipped up to prevent Mega's stupid automatic copyright blocking.

Decode at https://www.base64decode.org/
